team-page-text:
Google is known all around the world. Everyone is 'googling', checking on 'maps' and communicating in 'gmail'. For simple users, they are services that just works, but not for us. Developers see much more: APIs, scalability issues, complex technology stacks. And that is what GDG is about.

[Google Developers Group (GDG) Porto](http://gdgporto.xyz/) is an open and volunteer community who aims to gather people together to share experience about Google technologies.

Our goal is to organize space to connect the best experts around Porto with all the developers community.
